{"tid":1200711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【溫和X勇武】合作推翻惡法","createTime":"2019-06-10T21:05:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T05:17:23.000Z","uid":152321,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5a04a7bb1e8c94ba940145cfc21364f57fcfd57d","tid":1200711,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T21:05:42.000Z","msg":"認真個句，警察得個3萬人，我地幾十萬人兵分幾路絕對更有效率。 <br />\n溫和派嘅繼續你地嘅做法，罷工罷課又好，慢駛阻塞交通塞到林奠連門口都出唔到又好，其實同時間勇武派都可以去衝擊立法會。<br />\n<br />\n溫和嘅可以去呢個post到睇下有咩可以做到<br />\n溫和派合法抗爭！入嚟集思廣益！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1197620\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1197620</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我明白大家可能會覺得溫和派嘅做法無乜危險，大多數人都會選擇溫和做法。 但係我可以肯定香港人到咗生死存亡呢一刻，一定唔會驚危險，呢舖係背水一戰，一係成功反送中，一係香港收皮，我地要盡可能團結我地嘅力量。<br />\n<br />\n就算十一晚，十二號無返個一百萬人肯出黎，三、四十萬點都會有。唔理你係溫和定勇武，只要你肯企出黎，你肯反抗，你就係我地嘅一份子，你就係肯企出黎，不懼強權，拯救香港，拯救自己嘅家嘅英雄！<br />\n<br />\n我地比起班黑警起碼多十倍人，再加上我相信黑警𥚃面都有一啲反對嘅聲音，星星之火，足以燎原，可以減弱佢地嘅士氣。我地而家要做嘅嘢並唔係鳩衝，而係打一場仗！比起鳩衝，我地更如應該要用車輪戰，勇武派嘅，衝一輪，換人再上。溫和派嘅，斷鳩佢地嘅後援，補給。搞到佢地疲乏無力，然後先再總動員一齊衝。<br />\n<br />\n你可能話我on9，打得機多，邊有可能打機咁打。無錯，我純粹紙上談兵，我好希望現實真係咁易，但我知道無可能。所以我只係希望大家可以將所有力量團結一齊，用自己認為洽當嘅方法，表達自身嘅訴求。我相信，你唔會係自己得一個。我相信，香港仲有得希望。而希望就係掌握係你同我嘅手中。<br />\n<br />\n六月十一晚到六月十二， 一齊去拯救我地嘅家。"},{"pid":"ef97a8711fd0a655e1ed3147ea6d2865654b0c3d","tid":1200711,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T21:09:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"42365621a296ecf889b32a8b613dcf827498ac74","tid":1200711,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T21:25:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1188c5b2288ab6d9c61ed934468c5a3e13d0e4f5","tid":1200711,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T21:27:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1ffbc9310a486b2b2683f9669dd7aa4924bb1809","tid":1200711,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T21:29:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6850be4ecdcc44a23adf08d8efd5ca4e18e1785a","tid":1200711,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T21:32:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"93e5a391e96e9fa5a75d1e0a6ef5128f4115281c","tid":1200711,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T21:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca12bd3b265e9c61718b4d2c1b639d663ad1646d","tid":1200711,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T21:37:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5bcd5bbc9f8e693878e8ffcbcd337a9f0d7f782","tid":1200711,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T21:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae10e8955fac16f4cd6ec4f4e82f743759d32caf","tid":1200711,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3064cf264592452aadc6a7938b97f35f04306411","tid":1200711,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46fabca05c674493a607d8cbf8caaf146febded2","tid":1200711,"uid":135517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbda63267b6f8d30b76956d17cd989c6f10d0b19","tid":1200711,"uid":241310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NifzLR3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNifzLR3.jpg&h=5e78dfc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以嘅話晒你幾秒鐘，入去留個言，可以嘅話叫多啲朋友來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n〔置頂〕唔通溫和派就無嘢可以做？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1199622/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1199622/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小弟通知咗大家我聽日會去同朋友拎錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果順路可以join埋，<strong>中環所有銀行</strong>都有總行，你拎港紙／美金都無所謂，甚至問開戶詳情都得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最鍾意<strong>多人喺中環</strong>來睇我拎錢，你唔撳都可以來睇<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好問有無用</span><br />\n<br />\n利申：非鍵戰，就算聽日得我同朋友同記者都照去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n我哩個係新自發嘅行動，想畀更多人知道<br />\n哩個活動十分低成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係需要你排一排隊，去撳錢；<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果多人，甚至可能撳唔到錢</span></strong><br />\n適合有包袱，又想做嘢嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<strong>散播虛假消息係犯法</strong>，唔好為咗更多人來睇「我」撳錢，就去作料！<br />\n已經搵咗記者朋友，歡迎大家繼續share出去！<br />\n同時唔好煽動其他人！其他人陣間見到都去撳錢就&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n可能有人唔認同，覺得我做嘅杯水車薪，但唔做過又點知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d199b443b7fe78c90ad8e5eda54a07bd1a78189b","tid":1200711,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:19:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d8a7281e4fe2196a21a3eb000ac65da8103983","tid":1200711,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:22:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各位原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港宜家正值歷史危機當前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我有少少嘢想同大家講</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>唔想勇武咪和理非囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唱聖詩又好，想成隊百人管弦樂團一齊奏交響曲都得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持市民大眾繼續不斷以合法方式反送中</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一百萬人遊行只係個開始，大家仲有好多好多嘢可以做，例如今晚開始直到12號喺政總舉行嘅祈禱聖詩會，甚至更加有人提議罷工罷課等，我希望大家要明白一樣嘢，任何願意作出反惡法嘅行動都應該要支持！香港人唔可以再比三毛分化，和理非同勇武必須一齊合作，佔大多數嘅和理非請用盡一切合法方法反對逃犯條例，逃犯條例絕對唔可以通過，否則我地同下一代就會生長喺講句說話都要就住就住，擔驚受怕嘅環境之中，大家絕對唔可以比逃犯條例過到<br />\n<br />\n我地應該要接受香港和理非佔大多數呢個事實，大多數人都唔會衝始終法律後果太重，所以大家可以用合法方式全力阻止惡法，只要係合法渠道去反送中，我相信唔少人都唔介意做多兩步，有啲人可能覺得有啲和理非行動聽起上嚟好似好膠，但請唔好理人點做，只要記住大家都係反送中嘅同路人，我地就應該尊重同埋支持佢地，支持和理非不斷以各種合法途徑反送中。去爭取更多市民同國際社會反送中。唔好話無用，你去做起碼仲有1%會成功，完全唔做就絕對唔會成功。大家一定要盡自己可以承受到嘅所有後果同力量，以政府徹回逃犯條例為成功目標。請記住，唔好再鬧分化，和理非有和理非做，其他人有其他人做，兄弟爬山，各自努力。<br />\n<br />\n歷史例子：<br />\n柏林圍牆冧之前幾個月冇人會覺得有生之年可以見到冧牆嘅一日，03年23條同12年國教都冇人會覺得可以令政府撤回23條同國教，正如今次亦都冇人會覺得可以令政府撤回逃犯條例。<span style=\"color: red;\">再強調一次，唔好話無用，你去做起碼仲有1%會成功，完全唔做就絕對唔會成功。</span>"},{"pid":"04492b2b294f229a49bd24a6e6c8d25118830d51","tid":1200711,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:29:03.000Z","msg":"Up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267f0eecb2b3b4fc06b89998b9f66139b227874c","tid":1200711,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cb0409b18aeb7f5c6209ba7425448520003bbaf","tid":1200711,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:41:07.000Z","msg":"團結一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d73bee2d43d5768a49f89e68522db130db98a2","tid":1200711,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T23:02:52.000Z","msg":"以海濱長廊為大本營，搭大量帳篷興建大本營。分一部分人用車輛堵路，沿住龍和道，立法會道，夏愨道，添華道不停圍圈慢駛，同埋係行人路上大量行人慢行。務求無人入到去立法會大樓，兼且黑警無法疏導人流同車流。"},{"pid":"4203790cf9d7b0f2eaeed4a053b26f0bfde59916","tid":1200711,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T23:17:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d656f5be5cdc69830850744cc45beb4fa9dab017","tid":1200711,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T23:22:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b47e072389e265953aec30543bd2ea1dab4d027","tid":1200711,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T23:39:52.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b165d82945f49fd1b348bf84c746d59cd3ae5252","tid":1200711,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef254195a6ca11cdc0ac0ccbbfbc323013d398f","tid":1200711,"uid":93043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:43:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78857a3b57184fd4b1e3d68708ce23e03ec70395","tid":1200711,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fef254195a6ca11cdc0ac0ccbbfbc323013d398f","tid":1200711,"uid":93043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:43:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T01:19:06.000Z","msg":"唔係夠唔夠膽嘅問題，係呢個做法合唔合適而家嘅香港。勇武派本身已經少人，如果勇武派採取呢一個行動方式，我相信只會將人數唔多嘅勇武派再分裂，兩頭唔到岸。<br />\n<br />\n社會運動從來都唔係一少撮人就可以做到嘅嘢。當前最重要嘅嘢一定係團結，而唔係過度使用暴力，從而引起更大嘅武力鎮壓。"}]}